#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:1
msgid "Git Integration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:3
msgid "Background"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:5
msgid ""
"Currently, there are two approaches to managing AI modifications: git-"
"based solutions and checkpoint-based solutions. We believe the git "
"approach is superior, as it can effectively utilize existing IDE review "
"tools, provides a clear timeline, and has good rollback characteristics. "
"Therefore, we decided to have MoonBit Pilot use git to manage both manual"
" user modifications and agent modifications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:7
msgid "You no longer need to fear AI making chaotic code changes!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:9
msgid "Setup"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:11
msgid ""
"We introduce a configuration file for the first time. Create a file "
"`.moonagent/moonagent.yml` in your current project with the following "
"content:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:13
msgid ""
"# MoonBit Pilot Project Configuration\n"
"# This configuration file controls moon pilot behavior for this project\n"
"\n"
"# Enable automatic commits when files are modified\n"
"auto_commit: true\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:21
msgid "After this, restart and enter moon pilot for the changes to take effect."
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:23
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:25
msgid ""
"MoonBit Pilot follows a structured git workflow to ensure clean "
"separation between user and agent modifications:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:27
msgid "Detection Phase"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:28
msgid ""
"When you submit a requirement, MoonBit Pilot first analyzes the current "
"git state to detect any uncommitted changes. This includes:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:29
msgid "Modified files in the working directory"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:30
msgid "Staged changes ready for commit"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:31
msgid "New untracked files that may be relevant to your project"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:33
msgid "User Work Preservation"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:34
msgid ""
"If MoonBit Pilot detects that you have previously modified code, it will "
"automatically create a commit for your work before making any "
"modifications. This ensures your changes are safely preserved with a "
"clear commit message like:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:36
msgid "moonagent_pre_user work before implementing authentication\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:40
msgid "Agent Modifications"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:41
msgid ""
"After preserving your work, MoonBit Pilot proceeds with its own "
"modifications. It analyzes your requirements, implements the necessary "
"changes, and creates a separate commit with a descriptive message:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:43
msgid "moonagent_post_implemented JWT authentication with tests\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:47
msgid "Workflow Benefits"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:48
msgid "This two-commit approach provides:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:49
msgid "**Clear Attribution**: Distinguishes between user and agent contributions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:50
msgid ""
"**Safe Experimentation**: Your work is always preserved before agent "
"modifications"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:51
msgid ""
"**Granular Control**: Each change set can be reviewed, modified, or "
"reverted independently"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:52
msgid ""
"**Conflict Resolution**: Reduces merge conflicts by maintaining clean "
"commit boundaries"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:55
msgid "Managing Commit History"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:57
msgid "If you don't like these commit messages, you can:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:59
msgid "**Rebase**: Merge multiple commits into one using interactive rebase"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:60
msgid "**Rewrite**: Add your preferred commit message"
msgstr ""

#: ../../pilot/moonbit-pilot/git-integration.md:61
msgid "**Submit**: Create a proper PR for submission"
